run it back, find where the leaf is about to break off,

544
00:32:02,191 --> 00:32:05,426
and record rotation

545
00:32:05,426 --> 00:32:10,100
And I add a little flip there, because it felt right in the moment, wasn't even planned

546
00:32:10,100 --> 00:32:13,235
Stop, because I want to pan over, so I want to drag whole bunch of layers at once

