I don't quite like the parallax, so I adjust a sensitivity a little bit.

552
00:32:27,583 --> 00:32:31,686
Try out again. I like that better

553
00:32:31,686 --> 00:32:36,258
So I get ready to go. I run it back to the beginning

554
00:32:36,258 --> 00:32:41,130
so I can kind of get back into the rhythm of the piece.

555
00:32:41,130 --> 00:32:45,401
Leaf hits, I wait a bit and I start panning

556
00:32:45,401 --> 00:32:48,269
And I don't know how many frames I waited. I don't know how long it was

557
00:32:48,269 --> 00:32:51,105
I went when it felt right.

558
00:32:51,105 --> 00:32:55,278
So I panned over this winter scene and kind of slowed down to a stop.

559
00:32:55,278 --> 00:32:58,145
And then I run it back, because I want to do something with my bunny.

560
00:32:58,145 --> 00:33:01,478
Throw away these tools because I'm done with them.

561
00:33:01,478 --> 00:33:07,155
And wait until I think my bunny should move

562
00:33:07,155 --> 00:33:08,979
and he hops away.

